Agent: Bilkul, ab barah-e-karam apna TPIN batayen, jo chaar alag digits mein hote hain.
Agent: Yeh TP

Agent: Shukriya. Ab barah-e-karam verification ke liye apna account number batayen.

Customer: 2156-1158
